        "solutionText":  "氓聹篓 AgentRunService.run() 盲赂颅茂录聦氓掳聠氓聨聼忙聹聣莽職聞 requireRunnableStatus + claimRunnableTask + setStatus 忙聸驴忙聧垄盲赂潞盲禄楼盲赂聥氓聨聼氓颅聬忙聯聧盲陆聹茂录職盲陆驴莽聰篓 MyBatis-Plus 莽職聞 LambdaUpdateWrapper 忙聣搂猫隆聦 UPDATE agent_task SET status = \u0027CLONING\u0027 WHERE id = ? AND status = \u0027PENDING\u0027茂录聦猫聥楼氓陆卤氓聯聧猫隆聦忙聲掳盲赂潞 0 氓聢聶忙聤聸氓聡潞茅聡聧氓陇聧猫驴聬猫隆聦茅聰聶猫炉炉茂录聦氓鹿露氓聬聦忙颅楼忙聸麓忙聳掳氓聠\u0085氓颅聵盲赂颅 task 莽職聞莽聤露忙聙聛茫聙聜茅聹聙猫娄聛忙路禄氓聤聽 LambdaUpdateWrapper 莽職聞 import 猫炉颅氓聫楼茫聙聜",
        "patchText":  "--- a/src/main/java/com/codepliot/agent/service/AgentRunService.java\n+++ b/src/main/java/com/codepliot/agent/service/AgentRunService.java\n@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@\n package com.codepliot.agent.service;\n \n+import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.core.conditions.update.LambdaUpdateWrapper;\n import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.core.conditions.query.LambdaQueryWrapper;\n import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.core.conditions.update.LambdaUpdateWrapper;\n import com.codepliot.agent.executor.AgentExecutor;\n@@ -13,6 +14,7 @@\n     private final AgentTaskMapper agentTaskMapper;\n     private final ProjectRepoMapper projectRepoMapper;\n     private final AgentExecutor agentExecutor;\n+    private static final String ERR_MSG_DUPLICATE_RUN = \"Task is already running or completed\";\n \n     public AgentRunService(AgentTaskMapper agentTaskMapper,\n                            ProjectRepoMapper projectRepoMapper,\n@@ -28,23 +30,27 @@\n     public AgentTaskVO run(Long taskId) {\n         Long currentUserId = SecurityUtils.getCurrentUserId();\n         AgentTask task = requireOwnedTask(taskId, currentUserId);\n-        requireRunnableStatus(task);\n         ProjectRepo projectRepo = requireOwnedProject(task.getProjectId(), currentUserId);\n-        claimRunnableTask(taskId, currentUserId);\n \n-        task.setStatus(AgentTaskStatus.CLONING.name());\n+        // 氓聨聼氓颅聬氓聹掳氓掳聺猫炉聲氓掳聠盲禄禄氓聤隆莽聤露忙聙聛盲禄聨 PENDING 忙聸麓忙聳掳盲赂潞 CLONING茂录聦茅聵虏忙颅垄茅聡聧氓陇聧忙聣搂猫隆聦\n+        boolean updated = agentTaskMapper.update(null,\n+                new LambdaUpdateWrapper\u003cAgentTask\u003e()\n+                        .eq(AgentTask::getId, taskId)\n+                        .eq(AgentTask::getStatus, AgentTaskStatus.PENDING.name())\n+                        .set(AgentTask::getStatus, AgentTaskStatus.CLONING.name())) \u003e 0;\n+        if (!updated) {\n+            throw new BusinessException(ERR_MSG_DUPLICATE_RUN);\n+        }\n+        // 忙聸麓忙聳掳氓聠\u0085氓颅聵盲赂颅莽職聞 task 莽聤露忙聙聛盲禄楼盲驴聺忙聦聛盲赂聙猫聡麓\n+        task.setStatus(AgentTaskStatus.CLONING.name());\n+\n         agentExecutor.execute(task, projectRepo);\n         return AgentTaskVO.from(agentTaskMapper.selectById(taskId));\n     }\n \n     private AgentTask requireOwnedTask(Long taskId, Long currentUserId) {\n         // ... 忙聳鹿忙鲁聲盲陆聯盲驴聺忙聦聛盲赂聧氓聫聵\n     }\n \n-    private void requireRunnableStatus(AgentTask task) {\n-        // 忙颅陇忙聳鹿忙鲁聲氓路虏莽聰卤盲鹿聬猫搂聜茅聰聛忙聸驴盲禄拢茂录聦氓聫炉忙聽鹿忙聧庐茅聹聙猫娄聛盲驴聺莽聲聶忙聢聳氓聢聽茅聶陇\n-    }\n-\n-    private void claimRunnableTask(Long taskId, Long currentUserId) {\n-        // 忙颅陇忙聳鹿忙鲁聲氓路虏莽聰卤盲鹿聬猫搂聜茅聰聛忙聸驴盲禄拢茂录聦氓聫炉忙聽鹿忙聧庐茅聹聙猫娄聛盲驴聺莽聲聶忙聢聳氓聢聽茅聶陇\n-    }\n-\n     // 氓\u0085露盲陆聶忙聳鹿忙鲁聲盲驴聺忙聦聛盲赂聧氓聫聵\n }",
